7) Programa de login + SCSS
-----
HTML
-----
<form>
  <input type="email" placeholder="Email">
  <input type="password" placeholder="Senha">
  <button>Entrar</button>
</form>

------
SCSS
------
form {
  width: 300px;
  margin: auto;

  input {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    padding: 8px;
  }

  button {
    padding: 10px;
    background: blue;
    color: white;
  }
}
